  <bioghist id="aspace_d6e4b08791c03a6045f7200e8c3f0c2b">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>The Alpha Psi Chapter of Chi Psi Fraternity was established at Cornell University in 1869. In 1896, the fraternity moved into the McGraw-Fiske Mansion. On December 6th, 1906, the Chi Psi house caught fire, killing four fraternity brothers and three volunteer fireman.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_7f9148c09579a850f7be147a69fe4199">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Annual reports; histories, including materials on the 1906 fire; correspondence; financial records; personnel records; pledging materials; and photographs of Chi Psi Fraternity.</p>  </scopecontent>
